{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"f81b7913-5a8e-4bb1-adcf-27aa81cd26b0","content":"Good news — **.NET 10 `dotnet test` natively supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform**, so you **no longer need `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport`**. That property was a bridge for .NET 9 and earlier SDKs. In .NET 10, the new `dotnet test` communicates with MTP test hosts directly by default.\n\nYou only need to keep `EnableMSTestRunner` (which builds your project as an MTP-based executable). Here's the fix:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Sz4DJzhSLsacbtT7uJm7Qp","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01WqidNPm9WEpqkukFvVLo8K","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-dde00e7af9b74c99935c1fdd16200751/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-dde00e7af9b74c99935c1fdd16200751/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"3ae33eb1-646f-453e-8898-91684d876915","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) support in `dotnet test`.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` has native support for Microsoft.Testing.Platform. The key changes:\n\n1. **`TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is no longer needed** — .NET 10's `dotnet test` natively understands MTP-based test projects. This property was a bridge for .NET 9 and earlier to opt into the MTP integration with `dotnet test`. In .NET 10, it's the default behavior.\n\n\n2. **`EnableMSTestRunner`** is still required — it configures the test project to build as an executable using the MSTest runner with MTP support.\n3. Since .NET 10 communicates directly with MTP test hosts, I can remove the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property from the project file.","outputTokens":606,"requestId":"1BD4:BB4CA:21038F1:246A041:6A03CF18"},"id":"1cc04030-3a69-444a-9043-c3f9b8821de2","timestamp":"2026-05-13T01:08:51.366Z","parentId":"3f7183ed-f030-4748-a09b-f5271b8dfbc7"}
